ARC project
ARC aims to measure and quantify the impact of inter
organizational networks in resistance campaigns such as those of the
on short term outcomes and the prospects for longer term democratization

In addition to her his other research activities the postdoctoral researcher will be expected to contribute to two publications on the ARC project in collaboration with other team members one examining the impact of the participation of social organizations such as trade unions and religious groups on short term concessions by autocratic regimes and one on how the participation of these groups influences post
conflict institutions
